sentences: He was an assistant conductor at the Zürich Opera from 1966 to 1969.
He served as first Kapellmeister of the Stadt Buhnen Freiburg from 1969 to 1975.
He was music director of the Westphalian Symphony Orchestra from 1976 to 1985.
He was chief conductor of the BBC Scottish Symphony Orchestra from 1978 to 1980.
He was appointed principal guest conductor of the Belgian BRT Philharmonic Orchestra in 1987.
He died of a heart attack in 2014, aged 73.
